                            <comment id="13826361" author="ewertz" created="Tue, 19 Nov 2013 10:07:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mostly unit and system tests. All the structure for reading and passing the property around the system already existed, so is just needed to be added to the DataWriterImpl.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13826726" author="dkulp" created="Tue, 19 Nov 2013 17:42:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch is good for 2.7.x.  Current behavior would be retained, new property for new behavior.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For 3.0, I&apos;m going to change this slightly.   The current &quot;jaxb-validation-event-handler&quot; will apply to both reader/writer.   I&apos;ve then added a reader properly (like your writer property) that can be used to configure them separately.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
